[
  {
    "type": "Bug",
    "description": "代码变更中，在 `get_typed_annotation` 函数内，对 `ForwardRef` 实例的处理逻辑存在缩进错误。原代码中，`annotation = evaluate_forwardref(...)` 和后续的 `if annotation is type(None):` 等语句被错误地放在了 `if isinstance(annotation, str):` 的条件块内。这意味着，只有当 `annotation` 是字符串时，才会尝试解析 `ForwardRef` 并处理 `None` 类型。然而，根据提交信息，此修复的目的是处理 `annotation` 直接是 `ForwardRef` 实例的情况（例如，当使用 `from __future__ import annotations` 时）。当前的缩进导致对于已经是 `ForwardRef` 实例的输入，代码会跳过解析步骤，从而无法正确处理 `Depends`，导致功能错误。",
    "evidence": "文件: fastapi/dependencies/utils.py\n@@ -245,6 +245,7 @@ def get_typed_signature(call: Callable[..., Any]) -> inspect.Signature:\n def get_typed_annotation(annotation: Any, globalns: dict[str, Any]) -> Any:\n     if isinstance(annotation, str):\n         annotation = ForwardRef(annotation)\n+    if isinstance(annotation, ForwardRef):\n         annotation = evaluate_forwardref(annotation, globalns, globalns)  # ty: ignore[deprecated]\n         if annotation is type(None):\n             return None",
    "advice": "调整代码缩进，确保 `if isinstance(annotation, ForwardRef):` 块及其内部的 `annotation = evaluate_forwardref(...)` 和 `if annotation is type(None):` 语句与上方的 `if isinstance(annotation, str):` 块处于同一层级（即，都是 `get_typed_annotation` 函数体的一部分，且顺序执行）。这样，无论是字符串转换成的 `ForwardRef`，还是直接传入的 `ForwardRef` 实例，都能被正确解析。",
    "confidence": 0.95,
    "severity": "High"
  }
]

[
  {
    "type": "Bug",
    "description": "当直接使用TestClient测试APIRouter（而非完整的FastAPI应用）时，如果路由使用了yield依赖，可能会因为scope中缺少'fastapi_middleware_astack'键而导致AssertionError。这是因为yield依赖的清理逻辑依赖于该键，而完整的FastAPI应用会通过AsyncExitStackMiddleware设置它。",
    "evidence": "文件: fastapi/routing.py\n@@ -115,6 +115,11 @@ async def app(scope: Scope, receive: Receive, send: Send) -> None:\n             response_awaited = False\n             async with AsyncExitStack() as request_stack:\n                 scope[\"fastapi_inner_astack\"] = request_stack\n+                # Ensure fastapi_middleware_astack exists in scope even when\n+                # the router is used directly without a FastAPI app (which\n+                # normally sets it up via AsyncExitStackMiddleware).\n+                if \"fastapi_middleware_astack\" not in scope:\n+                    scope[\"fastapi_middleware_astack\"] = request_stack",
    "advice": "已修复。在路由的请求处理入口处，检查scope中是否存在'fastapi_middleware_astack'，如果不存在，则将其设置为当前的request_stack（一个AsyncExitStack实例）。这确保了yield依赖的清理逻辑有正确的上下文管理器栈可用。",
    "confidence": 0.95,
    "severity": "Medium"
  }
]

